description: This top 10% score Cooter purrs with a rating of 56, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 168, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 2 for North, Leverage for East, Stringalong for South, and Nine Lives for West. Cooter has the personality suit of punter. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Cooter [168 Votes, Top 10% Score]
